# out/ (the built static export) is intentionally NOT ignored: it ships
# committed in the repository so a plain `git clone` + `pip install` works
# with zero Node.js/npm install, and so it's present in offline release
# bundles built by scripts/build_release_bundle.sh. Rebuild it with
# `make build` after changing frontend/src and commit the result. See
# docs/airgap.md and docs/installation.md.
